<plot>Retro-style, animated short tells the story of a lonely beatnik who longs to make the hipster art scene and win the love of a cool beat-chick. When artistic block and deadline pressure threaten thwart his aspirations, he creates a robotic doppleganger to solve his problems. Unfortunately a half ton robot programmed with an artistic temperament is rarely the solution to ones problems.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?080366</url></doc>
